			"prompt_category": "Entry-Core",
			"prompt_sub_category": "AN",
			"index": 1,
			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "<anim name='Greetings_04'> Oh hi ${loopMember}, not too much </anim>. Long time no see. <break size='.5'/> <anim name='Emoji_Turtle' nonBlocking='true' /> Hey look what <pitch mult=\"1.3\">I</pitch><pitch mult=\"0.9\"> found</pitch>. <ssa cat='happy'/>",
