			"index": 1,
			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "<anim name='Dont_Understand_01' nonBlocking='true' /> Not much ${loopMember}, it's been a while since we've talked. <break size='0.5'/> <anim name='Emoji_Cow' nonBlocking='true' /> I was just thinking about cows.",
